{"tid":501641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人本身唔鍾意韓國野，但慢慢俾twice融化","createTime":"2017-12-17T05:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T08:30:43.000Z","uid":34489,"like":18,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"efdc5d5c894b0fd0f631b26c3a5617c66cdebda9","tid":501641,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"本身唔鍾意韓國野 衣著 歌 劇 食物<br />\n就算班fd成日話去追星我都好少接觸<br />\n直至個fd介紹我睇SIXTEEN<br />\n見到twice呢隊野<br />\n雖然9個女仔年記少少 但係已經唱歌跳舞都好好<br />\n望住佢地又有一種好青春既感覺 係其他團比唔上<br />\n9女仔個由選拔開始成長 互補不足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日放工就係睇下佢地黎緊有咩活動 或者上v睇返佢地d片<br />\n睇住佢地由冇人識到依家變左全球大熱 真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人好似我咁由反韓變做once<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">유정연 사랑해!!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/3261acd379d701ff69a846495c47469c/tumblr_oqgtixHhZE1uh7ri8o2_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F3261acd379d701ff69a846495c47469c%2Ftumblr_oqgtixHhZE1uh7ri8o2_400.gif&h=1ab49d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aRKuuuB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaRKuuuB.jpg&h=ed6be374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KoLnwyLx95Y/WBWA8J_sjII/AAAAAAAAAa0/Cww3GNFTIsMWhpvcNgHv2SdrCX7BJhaMgCLcB/s1600/07044edba856a831421e260b1c44b90a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-KoLnwyLx95Y%2FWBWA8J_sjII%2FAAAAAAAAAa0%2FCww3GNFTIsMWhpvcNgHv2SdrCX7BJhaMgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F07044edba856a831421e260b1c44b90a.gif&h=d77b8a61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbfc693b82f82e45ff53b0d5338786a9226f944c","tid":501641,"uid":53488,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"唱歌跳舞都好好<img src=\"/assets/